{"tid":1205681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個撚個掛住星哈利路亞 成車成車物資運入去比龜都冇人理","createTime":"2019-06-11T22:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T22:45:53.000Z","uid":46658,"like":4,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f2712acda1cd946480865510de8bf6b1cfa2d30c","tid":1205681,"uid":46658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:21:12.000Z","msg":"成晚淨係識星哈利路亞同玩鳩啲痴線佬 <br />\n大大條立會出面條街喺到又比人任行唔嬲 <br />\n淨係啲運鐵馬後面支欄比龜嘅十六噸貨車都幾架 淨係識得嗌睇車 你老母欄撚住佢咪冇車囉！<br />\n煲底出面大閘又冇人理 明明對家都冇心守 唔係叫你要主動衝擊 咁你人多反包圍下 等佢地調兵換人都冇咁順利都得掛？<br />\n唔係話你和理非唔衝唔啱 但你老味咩都唔撚做咁要你早一晚出黎做乜？<br />\n早一晚出黎唔係應該為咗幫日頭啲人霸定啲位先咩？ 等朝早要衝嘅有靚位衝 對家又啲裝備部備又冇咁足<br />\n咁而家同你冇出過黎有乜分別姐？"},{"pid":"48e6debc5ca94fcbfce0e543881f240a8f148064","tid":1205681,"uid":34676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:22:21.000Z","msg":"軍師大家等你去指揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c732cbb76229a57cab102ce74824ee1c1c5dd5","tid":1205681,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:23:02.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"ba2fbe3b059002b36d4019139a27a4e4467b4a71","tid":1205681,"uid":46658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h5OYCJY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh5OYCJY.png&h=b8ad6512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個個上撚晒裝 點打呀大佬⋯⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"5501c13d4231e2d55a869ccd66e7689cb2eaa0ad","tid":1205681,"uid":191815,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:25:30.000Z","msg":"原來差佬會坐普通van仔出入<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b212860504bb703e0577ec4a4b3fccfbe99a173d","tid":1205681,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-